description: Best practices for React applications
globs: **/*.{ts,tsx,js,jsx}

---
alwaysApply: true
---

- Use functional components and hooks for cleaner and more maintainable code.
- Implement PropTypes or TypeScript for type checking and better documentation.
- Use React.memo and useCallback to optimize performance by preventing unnecessary re-renders.
- Structure components in a way that promotes reusability and separation of concerns.
